test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (18 == 3)
 +  where 18 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x787676a90ec0>([8])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x787676a90ec0> = [[8], [8], [8], [8, 1], [8, 1], [8, 1, 8], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 16 == 8
 +  where 16 = <built-in function prod>([8, 1, 2])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
